rows.label: tlk44510182_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I imagine this must be intriguing to
you travelers. Ether from the Divine Beast
flows inside here.

rows.label: tlk44510182_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You can feel the energy just by
standing here, see? Isn't it warm?

rows.label: tlk44510182_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I make it my daily routine to offer up
prayers to the Divine Beast daily for the
bounty it bestows upon us.

rows.label: tlk44510182_01_msg0004
rows.name:
And of course to Adel our ancestor,
for the peace he brought to us all.
